"Just one more thing" On @realmoney The Fed Is A Joke * And their forecasts have been continually wrong-sided In a Council of Foreign Relations meeting in Manhattan, New York Fed President is saying that interest rates will stay low for a long time now. cnbc.com/2019/06/06/ny-fed-p…

Six months ago the Fed was on a path to three rate hikes in 2019 (something I vehemently disagreed with in my 15 Surprises) LINK Since then, 1Q2019 Real GDP in the US came in at +3%. Today the futures market implies that we are now on a path of two to three rate declines in
the next nine months. The Fed is a joke - a body of empty suits and wrong-sided economists.
